to run on edison:
First go into a spark job and start the cluster (either interactively or in the batch job do:)

cd /scratch1/scratchdirs/beehive/cxedisonruns
SCRIPTPATH=~/cx/sc-2015/cx_spark/src/edisonscripts

$SCRIPTPATH/runsmall.sh 960 16 0 5 ""   $PWD
$SCRIPTPATH/runsmall.sh 960 16 0 5 960  $PWD
$SCRIPTPATH/runsmall.sh 960 16 0 5 1920 $PWD

$SCRIPTPATH/runsmall.sh 960 32 0 5 ""   $PWD
$SCRIPTPATH/runsmall.sh 960 32 0 5 960  $PWD
$SCRIPTPATH/runsmall.sh 960 32 0 5 1920 $PWD

$SCRIPTPATH/runbig.sh 960 16 0 5 ""   $PWD
$SCRIPTPATH/runbig.sh 960 16 0 5 4800 $PWD
$SCRIPTPATH/runbig.sh 960 16 0 5 9600 $PWD

$SCRIPTPATH/runbig.sh 960 32 0 5 ""   $PWD
$SCRIPTPATH/runbig.sh 960 32 0 5 4800 $PWD
$SCRIPTPATH/runbig.sh 960 32 0 5 9600 $PWD



